<h2 style="margin:0 0 10px 0; font-size:22px; font-weight:600;">
    ⚠️ Underwriting — Conditional Approval
</h2>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:25px 0;">
    Hello {{homeBuyerName}},
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    Your mortgage application has received a <strong>conditional approval</strong>. This means it has been approved subject to the conditions listed below.
</p>

<table style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:20px 0; border-collapse:collapse;">
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Application:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;"><strong>{{applicationNumber}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Property:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{propertyName}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{#if reviewedDate}}
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Reviewed On:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{reviewedDate}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/if}}
</table>

{{#if conditions}}
<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    <strong>Conditions to satisfy:</strong>
</p>
<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0; padding:10px 15px; background:#fff8e6; border-left:3px solid #f5a623; border-radius:3px;">
    {{conditions}}
</p>
{{/if}}

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    Please log in to your dashboard to review the full details and provide any additional information required.
</p>

<a href="{{dashboardLink}}"
   style="display:inline-block; background-color:#19C2AB; color:#ffffff; font-size:14px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none; padding:12px 25px; border-radius:5px; margin:20px 0;">
    View Conditions
</a>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    Best regards,<br/>
    The QShelter Team
</p>
